Nokia today launched its three new Android smartphones here in Barcelona: the Nokia 3, Nokia 5, and Nokia 6. While the Nokia 6 was already unveiled by HMD Global &#8212; the company that purchased the rights to sell phones under Nokia branding, the other two phones are brand new.
  
